Summon a villager

/summon villager ~ ~1 ~ {VillagerData:{profession:farmer,level:2,type:savanna}}

Unbreakable Iron pickaxe

/give duckmister Minecraft:iron_pickaxe{Unbreakable:1b}

Summon Jasper, My horse
/summon horse ~ ~ ~ {Variant:260, Tame:1, CustomName:"\"Jasper\"", Attributes:[{Name:generic.maxHealth,Base:9999},{Name:generic.movementSpeed,Base:0.4},{Name:generic.followRange,Base:40}],Invulnerable:1}

Summon Persistent Tropical Fish

/summon tropical_fish ~ ~ ~ {CustomName:"\"Fish\"", PersistenceRequired:1, Invulnerable:1, Variant:?????}

Load Village Structures with Structure Block

  1. Place Structure block and set to load mode.
  2. Enter structure name (See options here: https://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Village/Structure#All_structures )
    * Generic structure: village/<biome>/<structure-type>/<specific-structure>
    * Example: village/plains/houses/plains_small_house_5  This would load the plains biome house called plains_small_house_5.
